00:11:24.192 --> 00:11:27.133
Now, also interesting musically,

00:11:27.212 --> 00:11:30.514
there are seven notes in an octave, A,

00:11:30.554 --> 00:11:33.475
B, C, D, E, F and G,

00:11:34.056 --> 00:11:35.636
audibly affirming Yahowah's plan,

00:11:35.677 --> 00:11:37.217
which is based upon seven.

00:11:38.149 --> 00:11:40.890
It is one which reverberates throughout

00:11:40.951 --> 00:11:42.230
his word in time.

00:11:42.270 --> 00:11:45.493
For example, there are seven Mow'ed Miqra'ey.

00:11:45.533 --> 00:11:47.375
They are Pesach, Matsah, and Bikuwrym,

00:11:47.414 --> 00:11:50.235
which Dowd fulfilled in thirty-three CE,

00:11:50.735 --> 00:11:53.317
Shabuwah and Taruwah, which are upcoming,

00:11:53.498 --> 00:11:54.379
one very soon,

00:11:54.418 --> 00:11:56.940
the other just seven years from now,

00:11:57.440 --> 00:12:00.942
followed by God's return with Dowd on

00:12:01.003 --> 00:12:01.462
Kipurym,

00:12:01.503 --> 00:12:03.163
the day of reconciliations and our

00:12:03.203 --> 00:12:04.544
re-entry into Eden,

00:12:04.585 --> 00:12:06.725
as I have discussed on Sukah.

00:12:07.830 --> 00:12:08.769
So consequently,

00:12:08.830 --> 00:12:11.791
