00:27:01.195 --> 00:27:03.017
However, in this case,

00:27:03.096 --> 00:27:05.038
the object of Yasha's intent,

00:27:05.538 --> 00:27:07.759
which would have been the devoted and

00:27:07.819 --> 00:27:10.402
reliant, are nowhere to be found.

00:27:10.882 --> 00:27:14.003
At least they weren't for three thousand

00:27:14.044 --> 00:27:16.224
years from that writing and two thousand

00:27:16.244 --> 00:27:20.448
years from the fulfillment.

00:27:20.468 --> 00:27:22.189
So from this,

00:27:22.269 --> 00:27:25.510
we can deduce that only those who have

00:27:25.550 --> 00:27:26.592
an affinity for God

00:27:27.328 --> 00:27:30.089
who are genuine in their approach to Him,

00:27:30.890 --> 00:27:33.010
who are willing to be observant,

00:27:33.590 --> 00:27:35.891
willing to trust and rely on Him,

00:27:36.250 --> 00:27:38.031
who are willing to engage in the

00:27:38.231 --> 00:27:38.951
relationship,

00:27:38.991 --> 00:27:41.093
making a contribution to the family,

00:27:41.792 --> 00:27:46.574
and who are devoted sufficiently that they

00:27:46.614 --> 00:27:50.474
will continue their work on behalf of Yah

00:27:50.694 --> 00:27:53.895
and constantly grow in that relationship.

00:27:55.517 --> 00:27:56.757
Only they can be saved.

00:27:58.003 --> 00:27:58.324
Also,

00:27:58.864 --> 00:28:01.025
for whatever period of time Yahowah and

00:28:01.164 --> 00:28:03.644
Dowd were surveying,

00:28:04.444 --> 00:28:07.905
which I think is from Malachi through

00:28:08.026 --> 00:28:09.566
twenty-five years ago,

00:28:10.586 --> 00:28:13.247
there was literally no one on earth that

00:28:13.267 --> 00:28:15.647
was prepared to benefit from what they

00:28:15.688 --> 00:28:16.107
were offering.

00:28:16.428 --> 00:28:20.568
The fact is that until about five or

00:28:20.628 --> 00:28:21.489
six years ago,

00:28:22.596 --> 00:28:25.138
No one knew that Dowd served as the

00:28:25.179 --> 00:28:27.339
Passover lamb or that he fulfilled

00:28:27.559 --> 00:28:29.661
un-yeasted bread by taking our guilt into

00:28:29.701 --> 00:28:30.061
shield.

00:28:30.442 --> 00:28:33.163
Not one person on the entire planet was

00:28:33.202 --> 00:28:34.443
aware of that.

00:28:34.743 --> 00:28:38.286
Not a person knew how God delivered

00:28:38.326 --> 00:28:40.807
salvation in concert with Dowd.

00:28:40.887 --> 00:28:43.148
If you don't know what they did,

00:28:43.209 --> 00:28:44.950
when they did it, how they did it,

00:28:45.510 --> 00:28:46.872
you can't rely on it.

00:28:47.332 --> 00:28:49.653
You can't benefit from it as a result.

00:28:51.909 --> 00:28:54.652
And we have a pretty well-framed time

00:28:54.711 --> 00:28:55.952
frame, if you will,

00:28:56.453 --> 00:29:01.058
as to when all of this recalcitrance,

00:29:01.680 --> 00:29:02.881
when there were no takers.

00:29:03.561 --> 00:29:06.345
And it is similar also through the prophet

00:29:06.365 --> 00:29:06.924
Yashayah.

00:29:06.944 --> 00:29:09.087
The prophet Yashayah heralds the arrival of

00:29:09.167 --> 00:29:09.307
the

00:29:12.568 --> 00:29:14.371
of this person who will be an observant

00:29:14.411 --> 00:29:14.830
foreigner,

00:29:15.991 --> 00:29:17.993
a tree of knowledge for God's people and

00:29:18.034 --> 00:29:21.718
his arrival as the voice of God and

00:29:21.837 --> 00:29:24.060
as the herald of the king.

00:29:25.674 --> 00:29:30.676
And it is quite clear that between the

00:29:30.757 --> 00:29:33.698
time of Malachi as the last prophet to

00:29:33.738 --> 00:29:36.818
the time that that individual arrives and

00:29:36.838 --> 00:29:38.579
begins to convey God's message,

00:29:38.640 --> 00:29:41.000
there is absolutely no one on earth that

00:29:41.040 --> 00:29:43.080
is responsive to Yahowah.

00:29:43.121 --> 00:29:44.321
God says routinely,

00:29:44.761 --> 00:29:46.942
I looked and I found no one.

00:29:46.982 --> 00:29:51.424
So what Dowd is saying here is affirmed

00:29:52.065 --> 00:29:52.464
by God.

00:29:54.300 --> 00:29:56.502
So from the beginning with Abraham,

00:29:56.883 --> 00:30:00.287
Yahowah has been consistent such that we

00:30:00.307 --> 00:30:04.470
should all be aware that when it comes

00:30:04.530 --> 00:30:07.894
to the Beryth covenant and the Miqra'ey,

00:30:08.134 --> 00:30:10.415
invitations to be called out and meet with

00:30:10.435 --> 00:30:10.715
God,

00:30:11.396 --> 00:30:14.619
the beneficiaries participate in their

00:30:14.680 --> 00:30:15.941
deliverance and salvation.

00:30:17.542 --> 00:30:19.924
This is not a place

00:30:20.612 --> 00:30:21.993
where anyone is entitled.

00:30:22.374 --> 00:30:27.059
This is not a situation where you can

00:30:27.119 --> 00:30:30.183
be a deadbeat and say, I want God,

00:30:30.263 --> 00:30:32.166
I want you to do everything, save me.

00:30:32.727 --> 00:30:33.989
No, it doesn't work that way.

00:30:34.750 --> 00:30:37.073
You have to make the effort to make

00:30:37.113 --> 00:30:38.454
yourself salvageable.

00:30:40.529 --> 00:30:40.710
Now,

00:30:40.730 --> 00:30:44.092
Dowd is thereby affirming that our

00:30:44.112 --> 00:30:47.433
decision to accept and act upon the five

00:30:47.473 --> 00:30:49.935
instructional conditions of the covenant

00:30:50.036 --> 00:30:51.537
and participating in it,

00:30:52.718 --> 00:30:56.779
and to attend the Mow'ed Miqra'ey that deliver

00:30:56.940 --> 00:30:58.401
on the benefits of that covenant,

00:30:59.121 --> 00:31:02.123
not only liberate us from the effects and

00:31:02.202 --> 00:31:03.644
institutions of man,

00:31:04.203 --> 00:31:07.306
but also enable father and son to deliver

00:31:07.686 --> 00:31:08.247
salvation.

00:31:10.164 --> 00:31:13.287
This is a treatise on what Yashayah

00:31:13.326 --> 00:31:15.167
deliverance means.

00:31:16.249 --> 00:31:19.590
Liberation and salvation not only go hand

00:31:19.631 --> 00:31:20.131
in hand,

00:31:20.851 --> 00:31:22.873
but one also leads to the other.

00:31:22.893 --> 00:31:25.233
You see, to be saved,

00:31:25.413 --> 00:31:28.056
we must first remove ourselves from the

00:31:28.096 --> 00:31:31.738
corrupting and corrosive influences of

00:31:31.798 --> 00:31:34.338
man's most divisive and duplicitous

00:31:34.960 --> 00:31:37.020
individuals and institutions.

00:31:38.680 --> 00:31:41.580
This is a lesson on the purpose of

00:31:41.622 --> 00:31:42.102
the Towrah.

00:31:42.961 --> 00:31:44.502
It is the will and desire of its

00:31:44.682 --> 00:31:48.845
author, his inspiration to liberate us,

00:31:48.944 --> 00:31:51.987
freeing us so that we might enjoy and

00:31:52.047 --> 00:31:54.508
capitalize upon our free will.

00:31:55.548 --> 00:31:57.529
This means of course,

00:31:57.589 --> 00:32:00.391
that Jews and Christians would both be

00:32:00.431 --> 00:32:03.833
wrong in classifying the Towrah's laws.

00:32:05.219 --> 00:32:08.362
They are not dictates to be obeyed.

00:32:08.801 --> 00:32:12.704
They are instructions to be learned from.

00:32:12.965 --> 00:32:16.568
They are guidance and teaching for our

00:32:16.588 --> 00:32:18.390
benefit.

00:32:18.430 --> 00:32:19.471
So just two words,

00:32:19.590 --> 00:32:21.893
and yet for those who recognize that

00:32:21.932 --> 00:32:24.556
Yahowah inspired Dowd to write the Mizmowr

00:32:24.615 --> 00:32:25.316
Psalms,

00:32:26.037 --> 00:32:28.419
they explain what Father and Son are

00:32:28.499 --> 00:32:28.838
offering.

00:32:29.799 --> 00:32:31.781
They lay out the path to a relationship

00:32:31.821 --> 00:32:32.942
within the covenant.

00:32:33.567 --> 00:32:36.608
and they reveal God's will for our lives.

00:32:37.170 --> 00:32:39.912
They demonstrate the connection between

00:32:39.971 --> 00:32:41.133
freedom and salvation,

00:32:42.113 --> 00:32:44.634
all while conveying the choice we are

00:32:44.674 --> 00:32:49.838
afforded and the benefits derived from it.

00:32:49.858 --> 00:32:52.961
As positive and uplifting as these words

00:32:53.060 --> 00:32:55.002
are,

00:32:55.022 --> 00:32:57.984
then what follows is even more tragic.

00:32:58.924 --> 00:33:00.646
And I think the whole thing is fairly

00:33:00.767 --> 00:33:02.268
sad because

00:33:03.250 --> 00:33:07.531
you know, God and Dowd, Yahowah and Dowd,

00:33:08.593 --> 00:33:10.413
wanted to offer a salvation.

00:33:10.452 --> 00:33:14.434
They did what they had chosen to do.

00:33:14.855 --> 00:33:18.215
They provided this opportunity for us to

00:33:18.256 --> 00:33:19.836
be delivered from harm's way.

00:33:22.557 --> 00:33:23.477
No one capitalized.

00:33:25.238 --> 00:33:26.938
And the more people became religious,

00:33:26.978 --> 00:33:29.659
the more they perverted what God was

00:33:29.739 --> 00:33:30.078
offering,

00:33:31.279 --> 00:33:31.839
making it

00:33:33.143 --> 00:33:34.124
unavailable to anyone.

00:33:36.125 --> 00:33:38.405
So as positive and unlifting as those

00:33:38.445 --> 00:33:40.866
first two words about them being in

00:33:40.886 --> 00:33:42.587
agreement to deliver salvation,

00:33:43.249 --> 00:33:45.750
the rest is awful.

00:33:46.951 --> 00:33:49.092
The reason as few as one in a

00:33:49.152 --> 00:33:53.634
million understand what Yahowah inspired

00:33:53.673 --> 00:33:56.336
his Messiah to write is that for a

00:33:56.375 --> 00:33:57.836
very long period of time,

00:33:59.017 --> 00:34:00.377
literally no one was listening.

00:34:02.155 --> 00:34:04.435
All of the prophets who revealed Yahowah's

00:34:04.496 --> 00:34:06.656
inspiration came after Dowd,

00:34:07.176 --> 00:34:08.836
with the exception of Moshe,

00:34:09.317 --> 00:34:12.257
Yahowsha ben Nun, Ruth, Deborah,

00:34:12.958 --> 00:34:16.659
and the king's contemporaries, Shamuw’el,

00:34:17.498 --> 00:34:19.599
Chanah, and Nathan.

00:34:20.838 --> 00:34:21.438
And even then,

00:34:22.239 --> 00:34:24.340
many of the books written thereafter are

00:34:24.420 --> 00:34:25.579
highly suspect.

00:34:25.820 --> 00:34:26.219
By the way,

00:34:26.239 --> 00:34:30.061
we should add to that Ethan ha 'Ezrachy,

00:34:33.663 --> 00:34:36.563
But there are lots of books that follow

00:34:36.824 --> 00:34:38.664
that were not inspired.

00:34:39.686 --> 00:34:41.827
Nothing in Ezra, Nehemiah,

00:34:42.106 --> 00:34:45.327
or Haggai demonstrates that they were

00:34:48.009 --> 00:34:49.610
inspired by Yahowah.

00:34:49.630 --> 00:34:50.851
As such, these books,

00:34:51.391 --> 00:34:56.432
along with Ecclesiastes, Esther, Job,

00:34:56.492 --> 00:34:57.514
Jonah,

00:34:58.715 --> 00:35:01.557
certainly Enoch and Ezekiel,

00:35:02.139 --> 00:35:05.320
they all fall woefully short of the Towrah's

00:35:05.360 --> 00:35:10.826
test for determining if a supposed prophet

00:35:10.865 --> 00:35:13.708
was speaking for Yahowah, for himself or,

00:35:14.228 --> 00:35:16.489
well, for the adversary,

00:35:17.710 --> 00:35:21.414
as in the case of Ezekiel.

00:35:21.434 --> 00:35:23.795
This would leave us with prophets such as

00:35:23.815 --> 00:35:26.797
ElYah, Ethan,

00:35:28.925 --> 00:35:35.951
Yoel, Amos, Micaiah, Zephaniah, Howsha,

00:35:36.951 --> 00:35:43.737
Chabaquwq, Yirmeyah, Yashaiah, Zechariah,

00:35:45.797 --> 00:35:46.458
and Malachi.

00:35:48.440 --> 00:35:50.222
And the last two on this list,

00:35:50.342 --> 00:35:51.842
Zechariah and Malachi,

00:35:52.983 --> 00:35:55.206
wrote between five hundred and four fifty

00:35:55.246 --> 00:35:55.846
BCE.

00:35:56.005 --> 00:35:58.128
We might have had Yoel writing in between

00:35:59.014 --> 00:36:02.577
but right around that time as well.

00:36:02.617 --> 00:36:06.621
This would be five centuries after the

00:36:06.661 --> 00:36:08.023
Messiah's initial reign.

00:36:09.023 --> 00:36:12.126
That was twenty five hundred years ago.

00:36:12.786 --> 00:36:15.668
And yet during this intervening period,

00:36:15.768 --> 00:36:19.112
there have been very few sufficiently

00:36:19.192 --> 00:36:21.934
dedicated to Yahowah to be trustworthy

00:36:21.954 --> 00:36:24.436
witnesses on his behalf, if any.

00:36:25.518 --> 00:36:27.059
And during most of that time,

00:36:28.246 --> 00:36:29.047
There have been none.

00:36:31.208 --> 00:36:33.068
It's only within the last twenty five

00:36:33.108 --> 00:36:36.230
years that this has begun to change.

00:36:36.250 --> 00:36:38.030
There has never been a shortage, however,

00:36:38.070 --> 00:36:41.112
of those willing to lie for personal gain.

00:36:41.713 --> 00:36:42.094
In fact,

00:36:42.173 --> 00:36:44.994
most civilizations and cultures have been

00:36:45.014 --> 00:36:46.516
shaped by them.

00:36:49.340 --> 00:36:55.543
men speak futile and worthless lies shower

00:36:56.045 --> 00:36:58.606
falsely and vainly deceptively and

00:36:58.746 --> 00:37:01.586
errantly this is a term that should just

00:37:01.827 --> 00:37:04.849
rip the heart out of jews because the

00:37:05.489 --> 00:37:05.969
system

00:37:06.690 --> 00:37:08.831
that rabbis developed with their

00:37:08.911 --> 00:37:10.952
diacritical markings to create the

00:37:11.012 --> 00:37:13.932
impression that Hebrew didn't have vowels,

00:37:14.112 --> 00:37:17.193
so that they could shape the message and

00:37:17.853 --> 00:37:20.034
could hide the pronunciation of Yahowah's

00:37:20.094 --> 00:37:23.076
name by changing the pronunciation of the

00:37:23.695 --> 00:37:26.036
letters comprising His name.

00:37:26.536 --> 00:37:29.057
That system is called Shava,

00:37:29.217 --> 00:37:31.139
where they replaced the wa sound with the

00:37:31.199 --> 00:37:31.878
v sound,

00:37:32.418 --> 00:37:34.380
and that Shoah or shava system

00:37:35.280 --> 00:37:36.701
is deceptive.

00:37:36.800 --> 00:37:38.661
It's even named deception.

00:37:39.123 --> 00:37:43.304
And yet that is the basis of the

00:37:43.344 --> 00:37:44.266
Masoretic text.

00:37:46.007 --> 00:37:47.568
So when he says that men speak in

00:37:47.648 --> 00:37:50.409
futile and worthless lies, Shoah,

00:37:51.411 --> 00:37:55.554
what God is saying is rabbis are

00:37:55.614 --> 00:37:56.094
worthless.

00:37:56.974 --> 00:38:00.717
They are vain, deceptive, and errant.

00:38:01.496 --> 00:38:02.157
They are

00:38:04.996 --> 00:38:06.978
filled with empty promises and false

00:38:07.057 --> 00:38:11.039
narratives.

00:38:11.079 --> 00:38:13.400
In association with his loudmouthed and

00:38:13.420 --> 00:38:15.121
immoral countrymen, reaʿ huwʾ,

00:38:15.141 --> 00:38:21.184
rea' can mean loudmouthed countrymen are

00:38:21.204 --> 00:38:23.226
just flat out evil, wicked,

00:38:24.206 --> 00:38:26.068
good for nothing, undesirable.

00:38:26.427 --> 00:38:28.789
But it's those who are wicked,

00:38:28.909 --> 00:38:30.530
undesirable and evil,

00:38:30.610 --> 00:38:33.552
even loudmouthed in the company of other

00:38:33.612 --> 00:38:33.931
Jews.

00:38:36.889 --> 00:38:39.371
They continuously speak with flattering

00:38:39.431 --> 00:38:42.612
and yet derisive lips and insulting

00:38:42.652 --> 00:38:44.032
praise.

00:38:44.494 --> 00:38:47.456
All of their praise for Hashem and G-D,

00:38:47.516 --> 00:38:50.476
where all they're really doing is trying

00:38:50.516 --> 00:38:54.159
to elevate certain rabbis to distinction

00:38:54.219 --> 00:38:56.780
and pretending that those rabbis are

00:38:56.820 --> 00:38:59.023
somehow prophets for a God whose name they

00:38:59.043 --> 00:39:02.425
erased and who they actually despise.

00:39:03.853 --> 00:39:05.634
And it's all an emotional appeal based

00:39:05.675 --> 00:39:07.434
upon a double standard,

00:39:07.635 --> 00:39:09.675
individual reasoning and personal

00:39:09.996 --> 00:39:10.835
motivations.

00:39:11.795 --> 00:39:14.056
Or so says the man who should know,

00:39:14.396 --> 00:39:16.157
Dowd, the very Son of God,

00:39:16.476 --> 00:39:18.597
our Messiah and returning King.

00:39:19.378 --> 00:39:19.918
And

00:39:19.978 --> 00:39:23.778
Mizmowr, Psalm 12:2

00:39:25.000 --> 00:39:29.221
It's quite a menu of insights, isn't it?

00:39:30.184 --> 00:39:33.326
So after saying that he and Yahowah working

00:39:33.365 --> 00:39:39.068
together agreed that they would deliver

00:39:39.148 --> 00:39:39.789
salvation.

00:39:40.809 --> 00:39:43.010
He tells us that there were no takers,

00:39:43.911 --> 00:39:51.094
that men were not willing to be reliable.

00:39:51.333 --> 00:39:52.554
They were not willing to make a

00:39:52.634 --> 00:39:53.514
contribution.

00:39:54.695 --> 00:39:59.217
They were not suitable.

00:40:00.358 --> 00:40:02.561
And therefore, for the longest time,

00:40:02.621 --> 00:40:05.786
no one took advantage of the offer of

00:40:05.827 --> 00:40:07.289
salvation that God was offering.

00:40:07.909 --> 00:40:09.371
And he goes from there to say that

00:40:10.452 --> 00:40:13.373
This is because men speak futile and

00:40:13.434 --> 00:40:14.414
worthless lies.

00:40:14.873 --> 00:40:18.193
And he used a verb that speaks of

00:40:18.534 --> 00:40:24.014
vain fraud and deceptive conveyance of

00:40:24.635 --> 00:40:25.936
religious pleas.

00:40:26.976 --> 00:40:29.735
That is the basis of the Masoretic text,

00:40:30.155 --> 00:40:30.516
Shava.

00:40:31.577 --> 00:40:36.317
That system of diacritical markings

00:40:38.137 --> 00:40:39.498
designed to mislead.

00:40:41.818 --> 00:40:44.378
And they do so in association, he said,

00:40:44.418 --> 00:40:45.998
with their loudmouthed and immoral

00:40:46.018 --> 00:40:46.498
countrymen.

00:40:47.298 --> 00:40:50.420
Rea Hugh, his wicked and evil associates,

00:40:50.460 --> 00:40:52.701
his good-for-nothing and undesirable

00:40:52.740 --> 00:40:56.400
friends with common ethnicities.

00:40:56.420 --> 00:40:59.061
They continuously speak with flattering

00:40:59.121 --> 00:41:02.543
and yet divisive lips and insulting pride.

00:41:02.583 --> 00:41:02.742
Boy,

00:41:02.802 --> 00:41:05.003
isn't that the truth of really all of

00:41:05.083 --> 00:41:07.503
these horrible,

00:41:08.224 --> 00:41:10.664
misrepresented religious...

00:41:11.882 --> 00:41:12.443
icons,

00:41:13.563 --> 00:41:17.686
the rabbis like Akiba and Maimonides and

00:41:18.807 --> 00:41:23.791
Paul, later Muhammad, divisive lips,

00:41:24.231 --> 00:41:26.954
insulting praise with emotional appeals

00:41:26.994 --> 00:41:28.675
based upon a double standard,

00:41:29.956 --> 00:41:31.137
individual reasoning,

00:41:31.177 --> 00:41:32.498
personal motivations.

00:41:34.438 --> 00:41:35.840
So there are two anomalies here.

00:41:36.840 --> 00:41:40.362
here that may simply be an artifact of

00:41:40.442 --> 00:41:43.023
ancient hebrew grammar but you should know

00:41:43.063 --> 00:41:46.085
them nonetheless each individual which

00:41:46.105 --> 00:41:48.746
means individual man was scribed in the

00:41:48.826 --> 00:41:53.028
singular form as was rea hugh his immoral

00:41:53.068 --> 00:41:56.190
countryman well both verbs were third

00:41:56.230 --> 00:41:57.630
person plural

00:41:58.496 --> 00:42:00.556
Now this may be Dowd's way of saying

